The paper focuses on the development and maintenance of cross-platform mobile applications using Xamarin, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. The paper also involves mining and analyzing data from Q&A sites, which could be categorized under software development (cs.SD) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper applies Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) for topic modeling, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR).
